query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS workflow_sessions (
  id VARCHAR(32) PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  type ENUM('ai_reasoning', 'memory_transfer', 'package_processing', 'w_matrix_training', 'vector_invocation', 'custom') NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('active', 'completed', 'failed') NOT NULL,
  title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  tags TEXT,
  started_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  completed_at TIMESTAMP,
  total_events INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  total_duration INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  total_cost DECIMAL(10, 4) DEFAULT 0.0000 NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX user_idx (user_id),
  INDEX type_idx (type),
  INDEX status_idx (status),
  INDEX started_at_idx (started_at)
)
